media:group.media:title: SPANISH A2: Also vs Neither
media:group.media:description:
[ESP] En este vídeo vamos a aprender la diferencia entre "también" y "tampoco"; son palabras muy similares pero se usan para expresar cosas diferentes.
[ENG] In this video we are going to learn the difference between "also" and "neither"; they are very similar words but they are used to express different things.
